{"tid":1159173,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［懷舊］分享下小學時期最愛又必備嘅文具","createTime":"2019-05-17T12:58:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-17T18:50:29.000Z","uid":167330,"like":35,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"d4961166424ee8922f7aa5eea0538a4f4bde926d","tid":1159173,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T12:58:34.000Z","msg":"話說尋日小弟嘅細佬(細我十幾年)就買咗呢舊刷膠返屋企<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Bn2fezA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBn2fezA.png&h=8be6e998&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來而家都只係賣5蚊，睇住佢滿足嘅樣，就諗返起細個嗰陣其實只要有單單價值幾蚊嘅文具就好滿足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢舊刷膠用嚟鬥chok係一流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />因爲曉旋轉"},{"pid":"a512050c68ce9d1888ded642198c4601e00fb644","tid":1159173,"uid":75785,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"一定係有哂機關嘅筆盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f43d2ccfc371bbc014f23d1013d77d9de0f9a1fa","tid":1159173,"uid":168180,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mrplayer.tw/photos/shares/fun_201710303/%E9%89%9B%E7%AD%86%E7%9B%92/59f7d6ae9a655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrplayer.tw%2Fphotos%2Fshares%2Ffun_201710303%2F%25E9%2589%259B%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%259B%2592%2F59f7d6ae9a655.jpg&h=57f56908&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a717bccac31fbae747ea54eda5d4a7f397dc61d","tid":1159173,"uid":167330,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"a512050c68ce9d1888ded642198c4601e00fb644","tid":1159173,"uid":75785,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"一定係有哂機關嘅筆盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2H65Ji.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa2H65Ji.png&h=a2a6b1d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小學嗰陣身邊個個都必備嘅航空母艦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我嗰陣用50蚊買咗返屋企唔捨得用，過幾日放學返屋企竟然俾細佬整爛咗，差啲即場喊咗出聲，然後呀麻即刻畀咗一舊水我去買過另一個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5ce9e34ce615ad8def529fbaf520a6634dc6d4","tid":1159173,"uid":242917,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6feddca8fcab6e784f9c5e9ada46c6edbda36a81","tid":1159173,"uid":167330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f43d2ccfc371bbc014f23d1013d77d9de0f9a1fa","tid":1159173,"uid":168180,"like":101,"dislike":2,"score":99,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:02:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.mrplayer.tw/photos/shares/fun_201710303/%E9%89%9B%E7%AD%86%E7%9B%92/59f7d6ae9a655.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mrplayer.tw%2Fphotos%2Fshares%2Ffun_201710303%2F%25E9%2589%259B%25E7%25AD%2586%25E7%259B%2592%2F59f7d6ae9a655.jpg&h=57f56908&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"俾你快咗30秒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb95fa9f4ecac653ac9c1680f36d96594c1a1d65","tid":1159173,"uid":212845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:04:13.000Z","msg":"香味墨水筆"},{"pid":"f2ce112190b7b9f298551389c18455a06970a89d","tid":1159173,"uid":243756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a717bccac31fbae747ea54eda5d4a7f397dc61d","tid":1159173,"uid":167330,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"a512050c68ce9d1888ded642198c4601e00fb644","tid":1159173,"uid":75785,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:00:14.000Z","msg":"一定係有哂機關嘅筆盒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-17T13:03:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a2H65Ji.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https:/